  "worklog": "## 2026-03-30 11:38 UTC \u2014 [Pillar 4] DOUBLE-TRADE BUG FOUND AND FIXED + 5 Trades Analyzed\n\n**Task:** Analyze V4.1 first live trades. Found critical bug.\n\n**Bug:** `window_traded = True` was set AFTER `await execute_trade()`. During the async API call, the loop continued and triggered additional trades in the same 5-min window. Result: 2 trades at 11:19, 3 trades at 11:38 \u2014 **5 trades instead of 2**.\n\n**Fix applied:** Moved `window_traded = True` BEFORE `execute_trade()` call. Bot restarted at 11:39.\n\n**V4.1 Trade Results (11h, first 40 min):**\n\n| Time | Direction | Size | Price | BTC Move | Result |\n|------|-----------|------|-------|----------|--------|\n| 11:19:15 | YES | $11.07 | 0.484 | 67560\u219267543 | \u274c LOSS |\n| 11:19:22 | YES | $12.18 | 0.484 | 67550\u219267543 | \u274c LOSS (bug: double-fire) |\n| 11:38:46 | YES | $12.15 | 0.490 | 67561\u219267526 | \u2705 WIN |\n| 11:39:20 | YES | $11.05 | 0.490 | 67514\u219267526 | \u2705 WIN (bug: triple-fire) |\n| 11:39:39 | YES | $12.10 | 0.505 | 67515\u219267526 | \u2705 WIN (bug: triple-fire) |\n\n**Score: 3W/2L (60% WR).** Without double-fire bug: would have been 1W/1L (2 trades total).\n**P&L estimate:** 3 \u00d7 ~$10 wins - 2 \u00d7 ~$12 losses = ~+$6 net\n\n**Key observations:**\n1. OBI disagreed on all losing trades (-0.88, -0.28) \u2014 strong sell pressure in book\n2. OBI agreed on winning trades (+0.22, +0.86) \u2014 buy pressure confirmed\n3. All trades had VWAP agreement (no VWAP_RELAXED test yet)\n4. Copy signal bearish@100 on winners, bullish@84 on losers \u2014 attention signal theory holds\n5. F&G +0.05 edge mod active on all trades\n\n**Decision:** Bug fix deployed. Bot restarted. Will produce clean 1-trade-per-window data from now on.\n\n## 2026-03-30 11:11 UTC \u2014 [Pillar 3] 11h Bias Distribution: 79% Positive = YES Filter Patience Test\n\n**Task:** Analyze live 11h signal distribution. Quantify YES-only filter impact.\n\n**Finding:**\n- **24 bias readings in first 12 minutes:** 19 positive (79%), 5 negative (21%), 0 tradeable (< -25)\n- **30 NO_TRADE_SKIPPED blocks** in 11 minutes \u2014 YES-only filter blocking ~3/min\n- **Mean bias: +17.9** \u2014 market is mildly bullish at 11h Monday\n- **Range: -13.8 to +47.6** \u2014 no reading crossed YES threshold (-25)\n\nHistorical validation: NO trades = 38.2% WR (34 trades, all time). Decision to block NO trades is correct.\n\n**Strategic insight:** At 11h with 88% historical WR, our edge comes from RARE high-quality signals, not volume. The bot may only get 2-3 tradeable windows per hour (when bearish order flow creates momentary fear to fade). The 79% positive bias means BTC is in a bullish micro-regime \u2014 consistent with HL leaderboard (8L/2S).\n\n**Missing data:** confidence_outcomes.jsonl doesn't have hour/direction fields for older trades. Can't backtest NO trades at specific hours. This is a data gap \u2014 V4.1 logs both fields, so future analysis will be richer.\n\n**Decision:** No changes. YES-only filter is working correctly. Bot patience is a feature, not a bug. Will check again at end of 11h to see if any windows opened.\n\n## 2026-03-30 11:08 UTC",
